{"tid":101540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發You are fired】Trump因拒絕執行移民禁令一事，辭退代理司法部長","createTime":"2017-01-31T02:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T12:00:57.000Z","uid":35221,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"556f0b800c299c766774f74b3f2fba8acdde5dfc","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"Trump Fires Acting Attorney General<br />\nBy MARK LANDLER, MATT APUZZO and ERIC LICHTBLAUJAN. 30, 2017<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/30/us/politics/trump-immigration-ban-memo.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Ftrump-immigration-ban-memo.html&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=62bb1006\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nytimes.com/2017/01/30/us/politics/trump-immigration-ban-memo.html</a><br />\n<br />\nTrump Fires Acting Attorney General Who Defied Immigration Ban<br />\nby Chris Strohm<br />\n2017年1月31日 上午2:26 [GMT]<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-31/trump-fires-acting-attorney-general-who-defied-immigration-ban-iykwkot4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F2017-01-31%2Ftrump-fires-acting-attorney-general-who-defied-immigration-ban-iykwkot4&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cdeefb77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-31/trump-fires-acting-attorney-general-who-defied-immigration-ban-iykwkot4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0845b44ef07e1eed96e1feef50cc030cc6ce04e6","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:47:30.000Z","msg":"Trump Fires Acting Attorney General Who Defied Immigration Ban<br />\nby Chris Strohm<br />\n2017年1月31日 上午2:26 [GMT]<br />\n<br />\nPresident Donald Trump fired the nation&rsquo;s acting attorney general as the repercussions from the president&rsquo;s executive order banning some immigrant travel to the U.S. continue to shake his administration in just its second week in office.<br />\n<br />\nSally Yates<br />\nSally Yates Photographer: Pete Marovich/Getty Images<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i6rYX0DxX9f4/v0/1000x-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.bwbx.io%2Fimages%2Fusers%2FiqjWHBFdfxIU%2Fi6rYX0DxX9f4%2Fv0%2F1000x-1.jpg&h=7795e568&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTrump fired acting Attorney General Sally Yates, an Obama administration holdover, after she said in a message to staff on Monday that the president&rsquo;s order was not consistent with the Justice Department&rsquo;s &ldquo;solemn obligation to always seek justice and stand for what is right.&rdquo; She added that, &ldquo;I am not convinced that the defense of the Executive Order is consistent with these responsibilities nor am I convinced that the Executive Order is lawful.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nWhite House spokesman Sean Spicer said in a statement Monday night announcing her dismissal that Yates had &ldquo;betrayed the Department of Justice by refusing to enforce a legal order designed to protect the citizens of the United States.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nThe Trump administration named Dana Boente, the U.S. Attorney for the Eastern District of Virginia, to replace Yates as acting attorney general, according to the statement.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-31/trump-fires-acting-attorney-general-who-defied-immigration-ban-iykwkot4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fpolitics%2Farticles%2F2017-01-31%2Ftrump-fires-acting-attorney-general-who-defied-immigration-ban-iykwkot4&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=cdeefb77\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/politics/articles/2017-01-31/trump-fires-acting-attorney-general-who-defied-immigration-ban-iykwkot4</a>"},{"pid":"df9948afb7b8e24b6e65d7624def7639050f1376","tid":101540,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:49:15.000Z","msg":"President good job<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb3cc30355775e37b4a89482f8ff71d7289d548","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:50:12.000Z","msg":"Trump fires acting AG after she declines to defend travel ban<br />\n<br />\nBy Evan Perez and Jeremy Diamond, CNN<br />\nUpdated 0242 GMT (1042 HKT) January 31, 2017<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/30/politics/donald-trump-immigration-order-department-of-justice/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump-immigration-order-department-of-justice%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6fb428af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2Fpolitics%2Fdonald-trump-immigration-order-department-of-justice%2F&h=b4e365d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/30/politics/donald-trump-immigration-order-department-of-justice/</a>"},{"pid":"64cd747622ec8ffb4c70603636fb988af3334cca","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:53:27.000Z","msg":"【唔聽話即炒】署理司法部長同特朗普唱反調 遭白宮炒魷<br />\n<br />\n最後更新: 0131 10:46 / 建立時間 (HKT): 0131 08:35<br />\n<br />\n (美聯社)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170131/large/1485830778_b642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170131%2Flarge%2F1485830778_b642.jpg&h=64b51c31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n美國總統特朗普的「入境禁令」面臨法律挑戰之際，署理司法部長耶茨（Sally Yates）周一指示司法部律師，不要為「入境禁令」辯護，因她認為特朗普的行政命令不合法，白宮隨即宣布辭退耶茨，改為委任維珍尼亞州檢察官本特（Dana Boente）當署理司法部長。<br />\n<br />\n耶茨前年獲前總統奧巴馬委任為司法部副部長，特朗普上任後要求留任署理司法部長。<br />\n<br />\n早前已有分析指，耶茨的指令很可能只屬臨時，因為特朗普提名的司法部長人選塞申斯（Jeff Sessions）上任後，很可能維護特朗普的政策。塞申斯的任命正等候參議院的確認。<br />\n路透社／美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n轉自香港蘋果日報網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170131/56242792\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170131%2F56242792&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=d98d068d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170131%2F56242792&h=b872bd0c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170131/56242792</a>"},{"pid":"aa67a126fc9713cdd1d3febd173c7bfc3e26c21b","tid":101540,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd26c5f1946f73c096638ad05b2f5fc864f1bb8","tid":101540,"uid":43655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:55:00.000Z","msg":"House of Cards"},{"pid":"869b5c6f82785fd66468efcc297ff6b45b7ccce5","tid":101540,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3df29f9670c4e602a1d32562ce529616a6d268","tid":101540,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:55:39.000Z","msg":"trump trump we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb6aa98ba2d6330962d40a07b09d25f03dab912","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:56:06.000Z","msg":"原來係前朝餘孽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645ab457424cfa0602a5da23c938b33d7eac6133","tid":101540,"uid":48767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8dd10266ea987b82bf638258a0a84269191c71","tid":101540,"uid":13170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"AG既職責本身就係幫政府defend, 而家佢唔肯盡職責, 其實侵仔炒佢都算合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be130908510e40dba47f865dae1ff15d9e78b3c2","tid":101540,"uid":22888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:01:34.000Z","msg":"加拿大先岩岩比人炸完 都講得出d咁既野<br />\n左膠真係利害"},{"pid":"e58efe437c3f6652630015774b1fbeea682b2685","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:04:15.000Z","msg":"White House statement on acting attorney general<br />\n<br />\nUpdated 0241 GMT (1041 HKT) January 31, 2017<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.cdn.cnn.com/cnnnext/dam/assets/170130212306-02-dana-boente-file-exlarge-169.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.cdn.cnn.com%2Fcnnnext%2Fdam%2Fassets%2F170130212306-02-dana-boente-file-exlarge-169.jpg&h=295c94f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(CNN)From the White House: Statement on the Appointment of Dana Boente as Acting Attorney General<br />\n<br />\nThe acting Attorney General, Sally Yates, has betrayed the Department of Justice by refusing to enforce a legal order designed to protect the citizens of the United States. This order was approved as to form and legality by the Department of Justice Office of Legal Counsel.<br />\n<br />\nMs. Yates is an Obama Administration appointee who is weak on borders and very weak on illegal immigration.<br />\n<br />\nIt is time to get serious about protecting our country. Calling for tougher vetting for individuals travelling from seven dangerous places is not extreme. It is reasonable and necessary to protect our country.<br />\n<br />\nTonight, President Trump relieved Ms. Yates of her duties and subsequently named Dana Boente, U.S. Attorney for the Eastern District of Virginia, to serve as Acting Attorney General until Senator Jeff Sessions is finally confirmed by the Senate, where he is being wrongly held up by Democrat senators for strictly political reasons.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I am honored to serve President Trump in this role until Senator Sessions is confirmed. I will defend and enforce the laws of our country to ensure that our people and our nation are protected,&quot; said Dana Boente, Acting Attorney General.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/30/politics/white-house-statement-attorney-general/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2Fpolitics%2Fwhite-house-statement-attorney-general%2F&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=2134bbb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2017%2F01%2F30%2Fpolitics%2Fwhite-house-statement-attorney-general%2F&h=fb1ad0ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://edition.cnn.com/2017/01/30/politics/white-house-statement-attorney-general/</a>"},{"pid":"9c7f1194d8a1c4aae677b130a8fd22808062fb03","tid":101540,"uid":5734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c2f4efdead56e96cb45a0d347beb5efe19170b4","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:05:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d9c2e67a25381a0d4528f71fa41327cb303b5a","tid":101540,"uid":2503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"侵侵就快要同Isis 開拖，ban哂Isis 有影響力嘅國家其實係好正常<br />\n<br />\n唔通就快同人打仗仲大開中門俾人入嚟炸你咩"},{"pid":"3a66ca3a0729e2a9c9f1f8261964b3fa2e55f5a8","tid":101540,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea9f8953fe0b47aa708a81d51d751cd3ade6c132","tid":101540,"uid":68981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:11:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b502d0c44bc2e034a3711a271f896af8bac5ccb","tid":101540,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  德政  期待戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nWW3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36be45b6d73908f2d011bb6d2bedfec995d1508e","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"【美入境禁令風波】公開唱反調　署理司法部長遭特朗普即炒 (03:01)<br />\n2017年1月31日 星期二<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170131/s00005/1485831751874SL4_6D0660E9D63985DE2A6024F60216556E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170131%2Fs00005%2F1485831751874SL4_6D0660E9D63985DE2A6024F60216556E.jpg&h=a66fb7f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖1之1 - （明報製圖／美司法部長官方twitter圖片）<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普27日簽署的行政入境禁令，在美國及世界各地均引起不少反彈。署理司法部長耶茨周一(30日)致函司法部員工，指不認為特朗普的命令合法，強調司法部不會為其辯護，不料旋即招來特朗普即時解僱。<br />\n<br />\n白宮發出措辭嚴厲的聲明，指耶茨背叛司法部，她拒絕執行保護美國公民的法令，總統已解除其職務僱。聲明又指耶茨是奧巴馬政府任命的官員，她不善處理邊境問題，而處理非法移民問題上的能力更是非常弱。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普已任命Dana Boente接替耶茨工作。<br />\n<br />\n耶茨在奧巴馬年代獲任命為副司法部長，在特朗普要求下暫時掌管司法部。她曾致函司法部員工，重申司法部的功能不單在法律上提出抗辯，更須闡明何謂法律，時刻追求公義，站在正確的一方。<br />\n<br />\n（華盛頓郵報/法新社/衛報）<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170131/s00005/1485830936726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170131%2Fs00005%2F1485830936726&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5031072d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170131%2Fs00005%2F1485830936726&h=63b553db\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170131/s00005/1485830936726</a>"},{"pid":"403f1da8256aeba53f1ad0c86778b31f9d572efd","tid":101540,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98cd58b122c98c213f9d67777a217bf904310766","tid":101540,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b5fde5931994f368d504548f9eeed3dd19488b","tid":101540,"uid":60941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218f36aa0ec245a543370fe7609b337e8126bc7b","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:40:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n畀你搞到我都用多左特大版ICON<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084fbcd6c5818a53c42680f0bae86db3db506c17","tid":101540,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd244c956cdaa11f5abfaac28900280283c0682","tid"